HEADWORD: Coextensive
<hw>Co`ex*ten"sive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Equally
extensive; having equal extent; <as>as, consciousness and knowledge are
<ex>coextensive</ex></as>.</def> <au>Sir W. Hamilton.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Co`ex*ten"sive*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
Co`ex*ten"sive*ness, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coffea</ent>⟦br⟧
